ComicInfo.Summary: Chuck is very surprised to see Rachael on the arm of the senator and then angry. Walsh turns up at the apartment disguised as a pizza delivery man. He subtly hints he can get Katchoo out of there. Kat refuses and says she has to see this through and has no plan as yet. At the function Francie catches Katchoo's eye and is stunned to see her friend in makeup and a dress. Kat drags her into a bathroom and comes out a few minutes later. Francine emerges blushing with a dreamy look on her face. Katchoo meets a reporter at the function and gives him the scoop on the entire scam which is printed in a major paper the next morning. Tambi delivers the paper to Darcy who is utterly devastated at her undoing. Tambi dispassionatly murders her with a shot to the face. then, dressing the scene, she puts the gun in Darcy's hand and takes a Polaroid. David attends his sisters grave and is reunited with Katchoo and Francine.
ComicInfo.Title: The Danger of the Night
